    "General AI, in contrast to narrow AI, possesses human-like intelligence and can perform a wide range of tasks and understand information in a manner like humans.",
    "This type of AI may surpass human-level intelligence and perform tasks better than experienced human experts.",
    "It is characterized by the ability to learn, communicate autonomously, and make judgments.",
    "However, Super AI does not currently exist.",
    "That type of AI has no memory, and the task is specific."
